	   <tr><td colspan=2>Another suggestion, depending on what lvl you are, often stuff that you are attacking (solo) will run away as they get low on life, so use back stab then too.&nbsp;&nbsp;I have been soloing a lot so far, but hey, I am only lvl 11 now (almost 12).  My back stab is now at 20 something i think.<br>i also sneak up on stuff and get the first blow from the back.  Grouping is a good way to do back stab but when you don't have a group, be creative :)<br><br>Bemuser<br>Dark Elf Rogue<br>Tarrew Marr Server<br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
