	   <tr><td colspan=2>setting an Evade Hotkey would help too;<br>Rogues, know this;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>EVADE=HIDING DURING COMBAT TO ERASE/DECSREASE AGGRO<br><br>Easy yes? no, because you cannont hide+attack at the same time, so...do this;<br>goto Socials, set up a new key, i labled mine "EVADE" fittingly, and put the following lines in;<br>/attack off<br>/do 1<br><br>where "do 1" reffers to your abilities slots, make sure you put the number corresponding with BS. Hit it ONLY when you are with someone else meleeing, it will NOT work going solo.  Simply hit the Evade key, presto, Aggro erased, mob turns its back you attack+BS<br><br>This works very well with increasing Pickpocket skill too, i set mine up as follows;<br>/attack off<br>/do 6  (6 reffers to the PP slot in abilities)<br>/attack on<br><br>This takes little to no time out of fighting and turns 3 buttons into 1  &gt;) <br><br>Letum<br>Fennin Ro<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
